<section class="proje">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="header text-center"><span>Galata</span></h1>
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-md-10 col-xs-12">
        <div class="proje-info">
          <p class="text p-skills"> Ruby | Ruby on Rails | Html | Css | Geocoder | JavaScript | Cloudinary | Heroku | PostgreSQL | Devise | Mapbox API | WebSockets | Figma</p>
          <p class="text"> Galata is a mobile app built in a team of three from scratch in two weeks as our final project during
           a web development bootcamp at Le Wagon Istanbul in early 2021.</p>
           <p class="text">Galata is a tour guide for spontaneous travellers on a budget who interests discover sites around them with related audios, videos, photos and
           articles that upload from other Galata users and who also want to interact with other users.</p>
          <div class="project-btn">
            <%= link_to "See Project", 'https://galata-b567.herokuapp.com/', target: 'blank', class: 'btn' %>
            <%= link_to "See Code", 'https://github.com/issamok3/galata', target: 'blank', class: 'btn' %>
          </div>
        </div>
