              <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="17"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
              <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="assets/galata/root.png" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Galata allows travels search sites near them with different options like filtering by categories, address, and current location.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="assets/galata/filter.png" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="assets/galata/map.png" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Travellers can connets other traveller via avatar on the Mapbox and also they can click the site fro  Mapbox.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="assets/galata/loader.png" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>When Users clicked the search by location button, rainbow loader activated by JavaScript untill the find current latitude-longitude of the User's location is calculated using Geocoder and show near users and sites on a Mapbox.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="assets/galata/index.png" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Users can see sites near them with description and amount of the related contents.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="assets/galata/show.png" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Users can choice contents related sites.</p>
                  <p> Audios, videos embedded from spotify and youtube and photos which is uploaded to Coudinary and URLs are stored in the PostSQL database.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="assets/galata/contents.png" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Each of the contents icon made on Figma and used on website with  `svg` tag</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="assets/galata/videos.png" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Users can see each of the embedded videos from youtube etc. and they can watch the video on the same page.</p>
                  <p>And users can like videos and save the video on Liked Content page.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="assets/galata/articles.png" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Users can see each article with title and users avatar. Each of the article has been stored in the PostSQL database.</p>
                  <p>And users can like article and save the article on Liked Content page and they can read later.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="assets/galata/article.png" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="assets/galata/photos.png" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Users can see related photos of sites on Boorstrap Carousel and like the photo.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="assets/galata/audios.png" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Users can see each of the embedded audios from spotify and they can listen without leaving the page.</p>
                  <p>And users can like audios and save the audio on Liked Content page.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="assets/galata/likedcontents.png" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Users can see all contents that like</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="assets/galata/uploads.png" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>User can see their uploads and also they can uploads new content about selected sites. Each uploads store in the PostSQL database.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="assets/galata/upload.png" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="assets/galata/settings.png" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Galata users can cedit information and change the range.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="assets/galata/notifications.png" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Using WebSockets, users are notified on top of the avatar each time that get the new message from other users.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="assets/galata/burger-navbar.png" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="assets/galata/messages.png" class="d-block carousel-img" alt="...">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                  <p>Using WebSockets, users can start conversation with each other from the massages tab or from user marker on the MapBox.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
